SELECT
    toDate(event_date) as t, 
    countIf(largest_contentful_paint <= 2500) as good,
    countIf(largest_contentful_paint > 2500 AND largest_contentful_paint <= 4000) as needs_improvement,
    countIf(largest_contentful_paint > 4000) as poor

FROM $table

WHERE
    $timeFilter
    AND event_type = 'visit_page'
    AND browser_name = 'Chrome Mobile'
    AND largest_contentful_paint is not null
    $conditionalTest(AND hostname in($hostname), $hostname)
GROUP BY t
